of the past year have led the airlines in number of complaints 
showed a sharp improvement with their july figures continental had 
its best month in a year with 994 complaints per 100000 
passengers and northwest had 62 rate of complaints 
the august complaint statistics were released along with the 
july ontime statistics 
the number of mishandled bags increased slightly during july to 
715 per 1000 boardings from 676 in june twa had the highest 
number of such complaints 1165 for every 1000 boardings 
