after lenins death the article said the soviet founders 
appraisal of trotsky as a selfconfident perennially dodging and 
shifting and tricky politician became confirmed 
after being expelled from the party and the country trotsky 
slipped down to antisoviet and antimarxist positions the 
pravda article said 
