ceasefire in the iraniraq war the ceasefire began aug 20 
iraq has declared amnesty for the kurds reportedly at turkeys 
urging but kurdish leaders have already said they will not accept 
the promised pardon 
the kurds have not struggled to be pardoned but to achieve 
their national and democratic rights within autonomy said 
