the major rebel groups in iraq our struggle will continue until 
these goals are fulfilled 
the refugees originally spread along a 60mile stretch of land 
a few miles from the iraqi border are being resettled in tent 
cities set up at five locations in diyarbakir mardin and hakkari 
provinces 
protecting the refugees against the cold feeding them and 
providing for medical and other needs will severely strain turkeys 
resources which are scarcely sufficient for its own population in 
the backward eastern region commentators in turkish newspapers 
said 
