chissano will underscore the improving relations between the 
longhostile countries although mozambique continues to charge 
that south africa supports an 11yearold guerrilla insurgency in 
mozambique 
botha during his 10 years as head of south africas 
whitecontrolled government has paid an official visit to 
swaziland and made a secret visit to south african troops fighting 
in angola 
but he has not made an official state visit to neighboring 
botswana mozambique or zimbabwe three of the socalled frontline 
